[b]Description[/b]
Assembling made on the basis of the original image from MSDN. Languages have been integrated: English, Russian, and updates on June 13, 2017, together with MetroUI applications (13/06/2017). The distribution included Net Framework 3.5 (includes .NET 2.0 and 3.0). The system is fully on the original installer. Possible to establish from under BIOS, and out of the system.

Software Version: 10.0.14393.1358 / v17.06.14
assembly Author: Adguard
Language: English, Russian
Activation Status :- Not Activated

[b]Main Features :- [/b]
- Integrated update on June 13, 2017;
- Updated MetroUI application to build the release date (13.06.2017);
- Integrated NET Framework 3.5 (includes .NET 2.0 and 3.0);
- Integrate language packs: English, Russian;
- Cleaned folder: WinSxS  ManifestCache and WinSxS  Temp;
- The systems were not in Audit Mode.
All changes are made with standard Microsoft tools.

[b]System Requirements:-[/b]
* Processor: 1 gigahertz (GHz) or higher.
* RAM: 1 gigabyte (GB).
* Free space on hard drive: 16 gigabytes (GB).
* Graphics card: graphics device Microsoft DirectX 9 or later.
* Additional requirements to use certain features.
* To use the touch features require tablet or monitor that supports multitouch.
* To access the Windows Store to download and run applications that require an active Internet connection and a screen resolution of at least 1024 × 768 pixels.
